title: Antillophos bahamensis
text:
Antillophos bahamensis is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a marine <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Nassariidae">Nassariidae</a>, the true whelks.
Description.
The maximum recorded <a href="gastropod%20shell">shell</a> length is 20 mm.
Habitat.
The minimum recorded depth is 400 m. The maximum recorded depth is 400 m.
